======''Rubus'' subg. ''Dalibarda''======
''Dalibarda'' is a {{fny-gloss|monospecific}} genus, here treated as a subgenus of ''Rubus''.  Its leaves superficially resemble those of violets, but its flowers and fruit are clearly ''rubusesque''.

