====Tribe Amygdaleae====
The {{fny-w|Amygdaleae}} contains cherries, plums, and peaches, all three of which are in the genus '''''{{fny-w|Prunus}}'''''. 

=====Genus ''Prunus''=====

The genus '''''Prunus''''' is here separated into three subgenera: ''Cerasus'' (cherries); ''Prunus'' (sandcherries and plums); and ''Amygdalus'' (peach).

