=====Genus ''Crataegus''=====
There are about fifty hawthorn taxa listed for New York, and all but a few are considered to be natives.

The subgeneric system used here for hawthorns is from the [http://data.canadensys.net/vascan/taxon/1047 Canadensys ''Database of Vascular Plants of Canada'' (VASCAN)].  Their data is based in part on the ''Flora of North America north of Mexico'', Vol. 9, (in prep).

